column2:
"Okay, I have your report, so everything's done.
Thanks for today. I can think a lot clearer now."

"I'm not too proud to admit I basically
get in the way most of the time. But if you don't
mind, maybe we can work together again soon!"

"うん、報告終わりっと。
今日はありがとね、いろいろ。
あたしも結構すっきりしたよ。"

"あたし、基本的に足手まといに
なっちゃうかもしれないけど
それでもよければ、また付き合ってね。"
